1
00:00:06,190 --> 00:00:09,670
♪Don't cry for me in sorrow♪

2
00:00:09,670 --> 00:00:13,550
♪My silence is only a disguise
for my defiance♪

3
00:00:13,820 --> 00:00:20,240
♪I stand alone in a forsaken place,
drenched in mud♪

4
00:00:20,370 --> 00:00:23,840
♪My name and my love♪

5
00:00:23,900 --> 00:00:27,850
♪Have turned into strength
and part of my memories♪

6
00:00:27,850 --> 00:00:33,860
=Madam=

7
00:00:34,060 --> 00:00:38,300
=Episode 19=

8
00:00:47,560 --> 00:00:48,400
What are you doing?

9
00:00:49,920 --> 00:00:52,160
Miss Lili induced a hallucination

10
00:00:52,720 --> 00:00:54,560
and made me relive the past.

11
00:00:55,600 --> 00:00:57,680
I couldn't tell whether
it was a dream or reality.

12
00:00:58,800 --> 00:01:01,000
That should be the Fox Clan's
Yin-Yang Spell.

13
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:02,480
I think so.

14
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:04,480
What have you seen, then?

15
00:01:06,280 --> 00:01:07,080
I saw what you,

16
00:01:07,520 --> 00:01:08,320
Chongming,

17
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:11,280
and the Black-robed Man
had done behind my back.

18
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:12,640
And,

19
00:01:13,220 --> 00:01:14,120
I saw Mingkai as well.

20
00:01:14,800 --> 00:01:15,600
Huh?

21
00:01:19,320 --> 00:01:21,400
Anyway, I've never
done anything to let you down.

22
00:01:23,720 --> 00:01:24,960
You did plenty of them.

23
00:01:26,320 --> 00:01:27,480
Who said so?

24
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:29,880
You were always the one
who initiated it.

25
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,520
What do you mean by that?

26
00:01:33,520 --> 00:01:34,920
You always initiated our kiss

27
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:36,750
except for the time
when you were wounded.

28
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,120
I was just anxious to save you.

29
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:39,480
I didn't take advantage of you.

30
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,680
You just detest me.

31
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,760
No matter what, I'm charming, elegant,

32
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:48,620
and quite the looker.

33
00:01:49,040 --> 00:01:50,720
Anyone else would've been elated

34
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:51,640
to kiss me.

35
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,660
You'd better know what's good for you.

36
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,000
I don't detest you.

37
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:01,320
Huh?

38
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:05,640
Thank you

39
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,920
for saving me time and time again.

40
00:02:09,440 --> 00:02:10,800
Thank you for liking me.

41
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:13,440
Thank you for keeping me company,

42
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:14,320
Aojue.

43
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:18,040
Are you poisoned?
Or are you under someone's spell?

44
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:20,090
I don't have any spiritual energy now.

45
00:02:20,300 --> 00:02:22,200
I'm not strong enough
to handle your torment.

46
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,720
This happened last time as well.

47
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,080
And, you stabbed me.

48
00:02:36,640 --> 00:02:37,880
Now, I'm afraid

49
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:39,600
and a little excited.

50
00:02:39,720 --> 00:02:40,920
It feels like I'm in a dream.

51
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,040
That hurts.

52
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:47,490
This isn't a dream.

53
00:02:47,541 --> 00:02:50,945
♪Things are easily forgotten with time♪

54
00:02:51,163 --> 00:02:54,792
♪Fireworks don't understand the sorrow
of the world♪

55
00:02:54,807 --> 00:02:58,480
♪They light up the clouds in the dark♪

56
00:02:58,480 --> 00:03:03,010
♪Hoping to reflect in your eyes♪

57
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:08,280
Yuzi!

58
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:10,160
Yuzi!

59
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:11,680
What's wrong?

60
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:12,920
Chief Wu is dead.

61
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:14,560
His body is in the courtyard.

62
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,720
The reporters are on their way here.

63
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:27,680
She's here.

64
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:28,200
Hurry!

65
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,200
Ms. Shan Yunshu,

66
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:34,960
may I know why Chief Wu's body
was found at your doorstep?

67
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,440
I have no idea.

68
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:39,860
Chief Wu had just
shut down Dongsheng Trading

69
00:03:39,870 --> 00:03:41,710
and was investigating
a smuggling case involving opium.

70
00:03:41,720 --> 00:03:44,040
Do you think his death
is related to that case?

71
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:44,800
Sorry,

72
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,280
I'm unsure about that.

73
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:47,320
Ms. Shan!

74
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:48,560
Ms. Shan!

75
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,600
Ms. Shan!

76
00:03:49,920 --> 00:03:50,720
Ms. Shan!

77
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,160
Ms. Shan!

78
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,800
Please let us off!

79
