108
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:40,120
Ms. Shan.

109
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:41,640
Ms. Shan,

110
00:04:41,650 --> 00:04:44,040
I, Mo Shenhai,
will atone for my sins with my life!

111
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:44,880
Mr. Mo Shenhai!

112
00:04:45,080 --> 00:04:46,160
