113
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:46,920
Let me die!

114
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:47,960
I'll exchange my life

115
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:49,600
for the peace of Mo City!

116
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:50,520
Let me die!

117
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:51,840
Put down the knife!

118
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:55,200
The good will be rewarded,

119
00:04:55,220 --> 00:04:56,460
and the evil will be punished!

120
00:04:56,520 --> 00:04:57,640
According to my observation,

121
00:04:57,840 --> 00:04:59,720
Ms. Shan is possessed by a demon.

122
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:01,320
Let me

123
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:02,840
deliver Ms. Shan

124
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:04,520
from the sea of torment!

125
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:09,440
There's a monster!

126
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,480
Help!

127
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:25,880
What is Mo Shenhai up to?

128
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:28,840
He knew that he couldn't defeat us.

129
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,480
He wishes to achieve victory

130
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,760
in the midst of the chaos.

131
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,400
If so,

132
00:05:34,520 --> 00:05:35,600
what should we do now?

133
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:38,080
The situation isn't chaotic enough.

134
00:05:38,090 --> 00:05:40,280
I'm afraid Mo Shenhai
has another trick up his sleeve.

135
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:42,320
A civil uprising.

136
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:44,920
What?

137
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:47,080
The Mo family was massacred back then

138
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,480
due to a civil uprising.

139
00:05:48,500 --> 00:05:50,590
Mo Shenhai took advantage of
the situation and slaughtered our family.

140
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:51,560
No one could rescue us.

141
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:53,000
Now, I assume

142
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:54,440
he's using the same trick.

143
00:05:56,300 --> 00:05:57,960
We don't have much
spiritual energy left.

144
00:05:58,440 --> 00:05:59,600
If that's the case,

145
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,290
this will be unfavorable for us.

146
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:02,320
If so,

147
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:04,240
we can only go into hiding for now.

148
00:06:04,620 --> 00:06:06,710
We'll explain ourselves
when the opportunity arrives.

149
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:07,480
That won't do.

150
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:08,610
Once we go into hiding,

151
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,680
Mo Shenhai will get his way.

152
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:13,440
By then, we won't be able
to explain ourselves.

153
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:14,760
What should we do, then?

154
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:18,440
We'll fight fire with fire.

155
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,760
We'll quell the rumors
with our own lies.

156
00:06:27,310 --> 00:06:29,310
Shan Yunshu's subordinates
are killing innocent people!

157
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:30,440
Everyone, run!

158
00:06:43,740 --> 00:06:44,740
Be careful.

159
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:47,000
What's wrong?

160
00:06:54,520 --> 00:06:55,440
Hurry and leave!

161
00:07:03,860 --> 00:07:05,920
The Black-robed Man
is Aofeng, my younger brother.

162
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,400
Do you wish to hear my tale?

163
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:09,680
He's pitiful as well.

164
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:11,720
He has done too many evil deeds.

165
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:12,800
Yunshu, everyone

166
00:07:12,810 --> 00:07:15,150
is saying that you're controlling
the innocent with your sorcery

167
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:16,630
and causing them to hurt each other.

168
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:18,300
It should be the work of Love Severance.

169
00:07:18,410 --> 00:07:20,990
Aofeng actually poisoned
the innocent to acquire the Dragon Pearl.

170
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:24,990
Is it the same
as the voodoo I was struck by?

171
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:26,120
Yes.

172
00:07:28,960 --> 00:07:29,760
Is there no cure

173
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:31,920
for this voodoo?

174
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:34,560
Not for now.

175
00:07:35,300 --> 00:07:36,590
Once the victim is struck by it,

176
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:39,520
Love Severance will become one
with their bloodstream.

177
00:07:39,530 --> 00:07:41,120
However, we can employ Hu Lili's method.

178
00:07:41,130 --> 00:07:43,030
We can suppress it temporarily
using special methods.

179
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:44,590
I've already tried my best to save them.

180
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:46,510
But I've expended
most of my spiritual energy.

181
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:47,560
There are too many victims.

182
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:52,960
I'm afraid this is the plot set up
by Mo Shenhai and Aofeng.

183
00:07:53,220 --> 00:07:54,990
They wanted you guys
to rescue the victims

184
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,280
and expend your spiritual energy.

185
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:57,160
After that, they'll deal with me.

186
00:07:57,640 --> 00:07:58,560
There's no need to fear them.

187
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:00,320
At most, I'll drink your blood

188
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:01,400
and kill them with my powers.

189
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:03,360
After that, you guys can lock me away.

190
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:06,000
By then, we can ask Hu Lili for help.

191
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:08,920
What method did Miss Lili employ?

192
00:08:09,400 --> 00:08:10,800
She infused her demonic aura

193
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,160
into your body

194
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,320
and fuse it with
the Dragon Pearl's power

195
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:16,080
to suppress the effect of Love Severance.

196
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:18,760
The main thing is
that Hu Lili isn't here.

197
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:19,920
Where can we find her?

198
00:08:20,320 --> 00:08:21,520
It's useless even if

199
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:22,560
Hu Lili is here.

200
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:24,600
There's only one Dragon Pearl.

201
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,400
And, it's inside Madam's body.

202
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:28,800
We can't save other people with it.

203
00:08:31,200 --> 00:08:33,800
I shouldn't have told Mo Shenhai
about the Dragon Pearl back then.

204
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:35,400
He resorted to such madness
because of that.

205
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,560
He'll find out
even if you keep it from him.

206
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:58,280
He's just one of Aofeng's pawns.

207
00:08:58,720 --> 00:08:59,680
The victims are acting as if

208
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,560
they've lost their minds.

209
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:03,360
Most of my subordinates are injured.

210
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:04,480
If this keeps up,

211
00:09:04,760 --> 00:09:06,240
not only will the people
suffer heavy casualties,

212
00:09:06,920 --> 00:09:08,960
but Yunshu, you'll also
have no way to clear your name.

213
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,880
Therefore, we can't afford
to wait any longer.

214
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,440
What do you plan to do, then?

215
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:16,800
I want you guys
to place complete trust in me.

216
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:18,600
Just follow my command.

217
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:20,440
Shan Yunshu!

218
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:21,440
Come out!

219
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:22,800
What sorcery have you cast on us?

220
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,200
Return my husband to me!

221
