- Show yourself!
- Show yourself!

234
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:40,880
- Show yourself!
- Show yourself!

235
00:09:41,160 --> 00:09:41,840
- Show yourself!
- Show yourself!

236
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:44,116
- Dear folks, listen to me.
- Show yourself!

237
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:46,520
I have something to say.

238
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,320
I know

239
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:51,320
that I'm not a noble person.

240
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:54,520
But the Chamber of Commerce
and I are indebted to Mo City!

241
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:56,560
Shan Yunshu

242
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:58,760
colluded with monsters and demons
for her personal grudges

243
00:09:58,960 --> 00:09:59,800
and plunged Mo City into chaos.

244
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:00,640
Today,

245
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:03,240
I'll uphold justice for the people

246
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,760
even if I have to die here!

247
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:08,698
- Excellent!
- Excellent!

248
00:10:08,698 --> 00:10:10,800
If she doesn't dare to show herself
due to her guilty conscience,

249
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,440
we'll set fire to her mansion

250
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:13,640
and burn her alive!

251
